    <string name="stock_data_requirements_body">A candlestick chart cannot be built from the current price alone; it needs historical open, high, low, close, and volume records. Vico only renders data already supplied to the app. Tencent and Sina currently provide reliable quote snapshots here, but not a reliable multi-timeframe US historical-bar contract. Because this local-only app has no project server or bundled market-data feed, select the optional Alpaca Live IEX source and save your own credentials in Me to load chart history.</string>
